  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/71141e71398346122e2e8b2cb8b6d1b2.avif?t=1749184917\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Writer's Rush</strong> is a dynamic writer simulator where you fight for literary fame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as an aspiring author aiming to climb to the top and win the ultimate Writers' Tournament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with unique rivals, each with their own backstories and goals, as you navigate hundreds of stories, creative choices, and surprising twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Write articles, fanfics, advertisements, translations, fairy tales, screenplays, and novels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique mini-games for each type of publication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/4b5b8d7f571fd1a2dedf830353be7088.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/4b5b8d7f571fd1a2dedf830353be7088.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/4b5b8d7f571fd1a2dedf830353be7088.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 distinctive stories with different climaxes and endings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Creative freedom — write in any style, from fantasy to horror.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 writers with their own biographies and personal storylines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 unique levels to explore and master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/f30d64c44ea0817bb69fd7942f1e6543.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/f30d64c44ea0817bb69fd7942f1e6543.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/f30d64c44ea0817bb69fd7942f1e6543.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse playstyles and multiple paths to success.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 collectible typewriters to unlock and use.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >69 book themes to choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different literary genres.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge other writers in literary duels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A perk system to shape your writing style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special publisher contracts and writing assignments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic rating and feedback system that evolves with your writing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/71141e71398346122e2e8b2cb8b6d1b2.avif?t=1749184917\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Writer's Rush</strong> is a dynamic writer simulator where you fight for literary fame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as an aspiring author aiming to climb to the top and win the ultimate Writers' Tournament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with unique rivals, each with their own backstories and goals, as you navigate hundreds of stories, creative choices, and surprising twists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/3c6dd31e28dcd98cfedfae0fce59f6ee.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Write articles, fanfics, advertisements, translations, fairy tales, screenplays, and novels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique mini-games for each type of publication.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/4b5b8d7f571fd1a2dedf830353be7088.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akama