feedback system that evolves with your writing.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.poster.avif?t=1749184917\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.webm?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745800/extras/798447ffd53dd62625362f5392159523.mp4?t=1749184917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
